<P 18>
   [$Mr. (^Page.^) $] Upon the outcry of Murder, I came out into the #
Street, where I found 
my Lord (^Mohun^) just Surrendring himself to the Constable; and     #
immediately I went 
to Mr. (^Mountford's^) House, and I found him lying all along in his #
