   [$Mrs. (^Browne.^) $] My Lord (^Mohun^) said, he protected her,   #
for if it had not been for 
him, the (^Mob^) had torn her in pieces; but if they had had a mind  #
to carry her off, 
they could easily have suppressed the (^Mob^) , for they had six or  #
