Friend^) . So saith Mr. (^Hill^) , (^I shall light upon this         #
Mountford^) . Why, said I, what hurt 
hath Mr. (^Mountford^) done you? Saith he, (^I have been Abused, and #
I will have my Revenge^) . 
So I went and told Mrs. (^Mountford^) of it. About half an Hour      #
after, or more, (^Mr.
Mountford^) came down, and when he came down, I saw him a little     #
before he came 
to them, and went to him, and would fain have spoke to him, but he   #
would not 
